  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It is a cross sectional study in which investigators will be recruiting patients of any sex
      above 12 years of age who will present to surgical outdoor with per rectal bleed.
      Investigators will then follow them through investigations to reach a certain diagnosis. Then
      investigators will be able to compile the data of diseases and their frequency, which are
      presenting with rectal bleed in their setup.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
